measures.name: Variance at Completion
measures.expression: [Budget at Complete Amount (BAC)] - [Estimate at Complete Amount (EAC)]

measures.name: Lifecycle Cost Variance % (CV%)
measures.expression: DIVIDE([Lifecycle Cost Variance Amount (CV)], [Lifecycle Performed Amount (CUM_BCWP)])

measures.name: Lifecycle Estimate at Complete (EAC)
measures.expression: [Lifecycle Budget at Complete (BAC)]/[Lifecycle Cost Performance Index (CPI)]
